Large-scale real estate scandals in Quebec
Officials from the Road Construction Office, major construction companies, fund-raising political parties and specialists from the Italian mafia tell us every day what they know about a great "system" in which the construction industry, civil servants, politicians, trade unionists and mafia are involved.
